                      Styles for the season                    Partygoers eager to make an impressive style statement this season can do their best to head toward the ongoing exhibition hosted by Earthy Myths. On display is Nomads, a Christmas collection of outfits and saris, inspired by world cultures. Keeping in mind the winter party mood and in tune with the trend of effortless dressing, it features simple, non-fussy silhouettes, appropriate for women of all ages. The designs are inspired by crafts and contours from all over the world and created in deep hues like blue, black, maroon and green. Inspired by the works of artist Mark Rothko, the saris are subtly dramatic and set against a delicate tonal sheen.            Event: A Christmas collection of outfits and saris When: Till December 28 (except Dec 25 amp; 26); 11 am - 7.30 pm Where: Earthy Myths, 8/2 Loudon Street, 2nd Floor	                    
